tika.dc.description: 10 Easy Pieces With Tenor Saxophone/Piano DuetsThis is a Tenor Saxophone sheet music book with 10 easy sheet music pieces. Each piece has two easy arrangements, one for solo Tenor Saxophone, the other for Tenor Saxophone and Piano when playing duets. The piano parts can be played on piano or electronic keyboard, they are very easy to play and are arranged to accompany the Tenor Saxophone.Contents:1. Home on the Range2. Can Can3. Daisy Bell4. Oh Susanna5. Bill Bailey Won't You Please Come Home6. Lightly Row7. Lullabye8. The New World Symphony9. Michael Row The Boat Ashore10. When The Saints Go Marching InCompatible DevicesThe digital sheet music in this book can be viewed on all tablet devices.My name is Michael Shaw, I hope you enjoy the sheet music in this book.
